  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003ETo keep our communication with the public clear and accurate, only designated spokespeople may speak on behalf of Neumo. If you are contacted by the media, politely decline to comment and direct the request to your manager, who will forward it to Marketing/Communications or another authorized spokesperson. Do not provide \u201Coff-the-record\u201D statements. When posting on personal social media, make it clear your views are your own, avoid sharing confidential information, and follow all company policies. Unauthorized statements or disclosures may result in disciplinary action, up to and including termination.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
